# --- requirements.md 结构硬校验（唯一性/外键归属）---
REQ_FILES=$(echo "$STAGED" | grep 'requirements\.md$' || true)
if [ -n "$REQ_FILES" ]; then
  while IFS= read -r rf; do
    [ -z "$rf" ] && continue
    aicoding_run_gate critical "requirements-integrity" validate_requirements_integrity "$rf" || exit 1
  done <<< "$REQ_FILES"
fi

# --- CR 影响分析硬门禁（Phase 00）---
CR_FILES=$(echo "$STAGED" | grep -E 'docs/v[0-9]+\.[0-9]+/cr/CR-[0-9]{8}-[0-9]{3}\.md$' || true)
if [ -n "$CR_FILES" ]; then
  while IFS= read -r crf; do
    [ -z "$crf" ] && continue
    aicoding_run_gate critical "cr-impact-matrix" validate_cr_impact_matrix "$crf" || exit 1
  done <<< "$CR_FILES"
fi

# --- Git-Hook 3: .env / 密钥文件泄露拦截 ---
BLOCKED=""
while IFS= read -r file; do
  [ -z "$file" ] && continue
  base=$(basename "$file")
  case "$base" in
    .env.example|.env.template|.env.sample)   continue ;;
    .env|.env.local|.env.production|.env.*)    BLOCKED="$BLOCKED\n  $file" ;;
    credentials.json|service-account.json)     BLOCKED="$BLOCKED\n  $file" ;;
    *.pem|*.key)                               BLOCKED="$BLOCKED\n  $file" ;;
    id_rsa|id_ed25519|id_ecdsa|id_dsa)         BLOCKED="$BLOCKED\n  $file" ;;
  esac
done <<< "$STAGED"

if [ -n "$BLOCKED" ]; then
  echo "❌ 检测到敏感文件即将被提交："
  echo -e "$BLOCKED"
  echo "   请将其加入 .gitignore 或从暂存区移除"
  echo "   （白名单：.env.example / .env.template / .env.sample 不拦截）"
  exit 1
fi

# --- Git-Hook 4: status.md YAML front matter 完整性 ---
STATUS_FILES=$(echo "$STAGED" | grep 'status\.md$' || true)
if [ -n "$STATUS_FILES" ]; then
  while IFS= read -r f; do
    [ -z "$f" ] && continue
    CONTENT=$(git show ":$f" 2>/dev/null) || continue
    FIRST_LINE=$(echo "$CONTENT" | head -1)
    if [ "$FIRST_LINE" != "---" ]; then
      echo "❌ $f 第 1 行必须是 ---（YAML front matter 起始标记）"
      exit 1
    fi
    HAS_END_MARKER=$(echo "$CONTENT" | awk 'NR==1{next} /^---$/{print 1; exit}')
    if [ -z "$HAS_END_MARKER" ]; then
      echo "❌ $f 的 YAML front matter 未闭合（缺少第二个 ---）"
      exit 1
    fi
    FRONT_MATTER=$(echo "$CONTENT" | awk 'NR==1{next} /^---$/{exit} {print}')
    if [ -z "$FRONT_MATTER" ]; then
      echo "❌ $f 缺少 YAML front matter 内容（--- 块为空或未闭合）"
      exit 1
    fi
    for field in _baseline _current _workflow_mode _run_status _change_status _phase; do
      if ! echo "$FRONT_MATTER" | grep -q "^${field}:"; then
        echo "❌ $f 的 YAML front matter 中缺少 ${field} 字段"
        exit 1
      fi
      VALUE=$(echo "$FRONT_MATTER" | grep "^${field}:" | sed "s/^${field}:[[:space:]]*//" | tr -d '[:space:]')
      if [ -z "$VALUE" ]; then
        echo "❌ $f 的 ${field} 值为空"
        exit 1
      fi
    done

    WORKFLOW_MODE=$(yaml_value_from_block "$FRONT_MATTER" "_workflow_mode")
    RUN_STATUS=$(yaml_value_from_block "$FRONT_MATTER" "_run_status")
    CHANGE_STATUS=$(yaml_value_from_block "$FRONT_MATTER" "_change_status")
    CURRENT_PHASE=$(yaml_value_from_block "$FRONT_MATTER" "_phase")
    CHANGE_LEVEL=$(yaml_value_from_block "$FRONT_MATTER" "_change_level")
    REVIEW_ROUND=$(yaml_value_from_block "$FRONT_MATTER" "_review_round")
    [ -z "$REVIEW_ROUND" ] && REVIEW_ROUND=0

    aicoding_enum_contains "$WORKFLOW_MODE" $AICODING_ENUM_WORKFLOW_MODE || {
      echo "❌ $f: _workflow_mode 值非法（期望 manual/semi-auto/auto，当前：${WORKFLOW_MODE:-<empty>}）"
      exit 1
    }
    aicoding_enum_contains "$RUN_STATUS" $AICODING_ENUM_RUN_STATUS || {
      echo "❌ $f: _run_status 值非法（期望 running/paused/wait_confirm/completed，当前：${RUN_STATUS:-<empty>}）"
      exit 1
    }
    aicoding_enum_contains "$CHANGE_STATUS" $AICODING_ENUM_CHANGE_STATUS || {
      echo "❌ $f: _change_status 值非法（期望 in_progress/done，当前：${CHANGE_STATUS:-<empty>}）"
      exit 1
    }
    aicoding_enum_contains "$CURRENT_PHASE" $AICODING_ENUM_PHASE || {
      echo "❌ $f: _phase 值非法（当前：${CURRENT_PHASE:-<empty>}）"
      exit 1
    }
    if [ -z "$CHANGE_LEVEL" ]; then
      CHANGE_LEVEL="major"
      aicoding_gate_log_warning "${f}: _change_level 缺失，按兼容期默认 major 处理"
      echo "⚠️  [gate:status-enum] ${f}: _change_level 缺失，兼容期按 major 处理" >&2
    else
      aicoding_enum_contains "$CHANGE_LEVEL" $AICODING_ENUM_CHANGE_LEVEL || {
        echo "❌ $f: _change_level 值非法（当前：${CHANGE_LEVEL}）"
        exit 1
      }
    fi

    validate_status_table_consistency "$f" "$CONTENT" "$CURRENT_PHASE" "$CHANGE_STATUS" "$WORKFLOW_MODE" "$RUN_STATUS" "$CHANGE_LEVEL" || exit 1

    if [ "$CHANGE_LEVEL" = "hotfix" ]; then
      aicoding_bool_is_true "$AICODING_ENABLE_HOTFIX" || {
        echo "❌ $f: _change_level=hotfix 但配置 enable_hotfix=false"
        exit 1
      }
      hotfix_diff_count_check "$f" || exit 1
      hotfix_reqc_boundary_check "$f" || exit 1
    fi

    echo "$REVIEW_ROUND" | grep -qE '^[0-9]+$' || {
      echo "❌ $f: _review_round 必须为非负整数（当前：${REVIEW_ROUND}）"
      exit 1
    }
    if [ "$REVIEW_ROUND" -gt 5 ] && [ "$RUN_STATUS" != "wait_confirm" ]; then
      echo "❌ $f: 同一阶段审查轮次超过 5（_review_round=${REVIEW_ROUND}），请先切换 _run_status: wait_confirm 并请求人工确认"
      exit 1
    fi

    # --- Git-Hook 7: 阶段出口门禁 ---
    VERSION_DIR=$(echo "$f" | grep -oE 'docs/v[0-9]+\.[0-9]+/')
    [ -z "$VERSION_DIR" ] && continue
    [ -z "$CURRENT_PHASE" ] && continue

    # 检查是否有阶段推进（对比暂存区 vs HEAD）
    OLD_PHASE=$(git show "HEAD:$f" 2>/dev/null | awk '
      NR==1 && $0!="---" {exit}
      NR==1 {in_front=1; next}
      in_front && $0=="---" {exit}
      in_front && /^_phase:/ {sub(/^_phase:[[:space:]]*/, "", $0); gsub(/[[:space:]]+$/, "", $0); print; exit}
    ')
    if [ -z "$OLD_PHASE" ]; then
      # 新建 status.md：只允许从 ChangeManagement 开始，禁止跳到高阶段
      NEW_RANK=$(aicoding_phase_rank "$CURRENT_PHASE")
      if [ "$NEW_RANK" -gt 0 ]; then
        echo "❌ 新建 status.md 的 _phase 必须从 ChangeManagement 开始（当前：$CURRENT_PHASE）"
        exit 1
      fi
      continue
    fi
    [ "$OLD_PHASE" = "$CURRENT_PHASE" ] && continue

    OLD_RANK=$(aicoding_phase_rank "$OLD_PHASE")
    NEW_RANK=$(aicoding_phase_rank "$CURRENT_PHASE")
    if [ "$NEW_RANK" -lt "$OLD_RANK" ]; then
      DROP=$((OLD_RANK - NEW_RANK))
      if [ "$DROP" -gt 2 ]; then
        echo "❌ 检测到大幅阶段降级（${OLD_PHASE} → ${CURRENT_PHASE}，跨度 ${DROP}），已阻断。请人工确认后再调整。"
        exit 1
      fi
      aicoding_gate_log_warning "阶段降级：${f} ${OLD_PHASE} -> ${CURRENT_PHASE}"
      echo "⚠️  [gate:phase-transition] 检测到阶段降级：${OLD_PHASE} → ${CURRENT_PHASE}（已记录）" >&2
      continue
    fi
    [ "$NEW_RANK" -eq "$OLD_RANK" ] && continue

    STATUS_CURRENT_REF=$(echo "$FRONT_MATTER" | grep '^_current:' | sed 's/^_current:[[:space:]]*//' | tr -d '[:space:]')

    run_result_gates_for_transition "$OLD_PHASE" "$CURRENT_PHASE" "$f" || exit 1

    if [ "$CHANGE_LEVEL" = "hotfix" ]; then
      continue
    fi

    # 产出物存在性检查
    GATE_MISSING=""
    check_gate_file() {
      aicoding_staged_exists "${VERSION_DIR}$1" || GATE_MISSING="${GATE_MISSING}\n  - $1"
    }

    while IFS= read -r required_doc; do
      [ -z "$required_doc" ] && continue
      check_gate_file "$required_doc"
    done < <(aicoding_phase_exit_required "$OLD_PHASE" "$CHANGE_LEVEL")

    case "$OLD_PHASE" in
      Requirements)
        aicoding_run_gate critical "phase-exit:requirements" validate_constraints_confirmation "${VERSION_DIR}review_requirements.md" "${VERSION_DIR}requirements.md" "${VERSION_DIR}proposal.md" || exit 1
        ;;
      Design)
        aicoding_run_gate critical "phase-exit:design-trace" validate_design_trace_coverage "${VERSION_DIR}requirements.md" "${VERSION_DIR}design.md" || exit 1
        ;;
      Planning)
        aicoding_run_gate critical "phase-exit:planning-coverage" validate_plan_reverse_coverage "${VERSION_DIR}requirements.md" "${VERSION_DIR}plan.md" || exit 1
        ;;
      Implementation)
        if [ "$CHANGE_LEVEL" = "minor" ]; then
          aicoding_run_gate critical "phase-exit:minor-review" validate_minor_review "${VERSION_DIR}review_minor.md" || exit 1
          aicoding_run_gate critical "phase-exit:minor-test-evidence" validate_minor_test_evidence "$VERSION_DIR" "$CONTENT" || exit 1
        else
          aicoding_run_gate critical "phase-exit:implementation-review" validate_review_summary_and_coverage "${VERSION_DIR}review_implementation.md" "${VERSION_DIR}requirements.md" "$STATUS_CURRENT_REF" || exit 1
        fi
        ;;
      Testing)
        if [ "$CHANGE_LEVEL" = "minor" ]; then
          aicoding_run_gate critical "phase-exit:minor-review" validate_minor_review "${VERSION_DIR}review_minor.md" || exit 1
          aicoding_run_gate critical "phase-exit:minor-test-evidence" validate_minor_test_evidence "$VERSION_DIR" "$CONTENT" || exit 1
        else
          aicoding_run_gate critical "phase-exit:testing-review" validate_review_summary_and_coverage "${VERSION_DIR}review_testing.md" "${VERSION_DIR}requirements.md" "$STATUS_CURRENT_REF" || exit 1
          aicoding_run_gate critical "phase-exit:test-coverage" validate_test_report_gwt_coverage "${VERSION_DIR}requirements.md" "${VERSION_DIR}test_report.md" || exit 1
          aicoding_run_gate critical "phase-exit:human-spotcheck" validate_human_spotcheck "${VERSION_DIR}review_testing.md" "${VERSION_DIR}requirements.md" "$STATUS_CURRENT_REF" "$CHANGE_LEVEL" || exit 1
        fi
        ;;
    esac

    if [ -n "$GATE_MISSING" ]; then
      echo "❌ 阶段出口门禁（${OLD_PHASE} → ${CURRENT_PHASE}）：以下必要产出物缺失："
      echo -e "$GATE_MISSING"
      exit 1
    fi
  done <<< "$STATUS_FILES"
fi

# --- Git-Hook 6: 交付关口条件拦截 ---
# 当 _run_status=wait_confirm 或 _change_status=done 时，检查交付必要条件
while IFS= read -r f; do
  [ -z "$f" ] && continue
  CONTENT=$(git show ":$f" 2>/dev/null) || continue
  FRONT_MATTER=$(echo "$CONTENT" | awk 'NR==1{next} /^---$/{exit} {print}')
  NEW_CHANGE_STATUS=$(echo "$FRONT_MATTER" | grep '^_change_status:' | sed 's/^_change_status:[[:space:]]*//' | tr -d '[:space:]')
  NEW_RUN_STATUS=$(echo "$FRONT_MATTER" | grep '^_run_status:' | sed 's/^_run_status:[[:space:]]*//' | tr -d '[:space:]')
  NEW_PHASE=$(echo "$FRONT_MATTER" | grep '^_phase:' | sed 's/^_phase:[[:space:]]*//' | tr -d '[:space:]')
  [ "$NEW_CHANGE_STATUS" = "done" ] || [ "$NEW_RUN_STATUS" = "wait_confirm" ] || continue
  case "$NEW_PHASE" in
    Testing|Deployment) ;;
    *) continue ;;
  esac

  VERSION_DIR=$(echo "$f" | grep -oE 'docs/v[0-9]+\.[0-9]+/')
  [ -z "$VERSION_DIR" ] && continue

  CHANGE_LEVEL=$(echo "$FRONT_MATTER" | grep '^_change_level:' | sed 's/^_change_level:[[:space:]]*//' | tr -d '[:space:]')
  [ -z "$CHANGE_LEVEL" ] && CHANGE_LEVEL="major"
  [ "$CHANGE_LEVEL" = "hotfix" ] && continue

  STATUS_CURRENT_REF=$(echo "$FRONT_MATTER" | grep '^_current:' | sed 's/^_current:[[:space:]]*//' | tr -d '[:space:]')
  if [ "$CHANGE_LEVEL" = "minor" ]; then
    aicoding_run_gate critical "delivery:minor-review" validate_minor_review "${VERSION_DIR}review_minor.md" || exit 1
    aicoding_run_gate critical "delivery:minor-test-evidence" validate_minor_test_evidence "$VERSION_DIR" "$CONTENT" || exit 1
    if aicoding_staged_exists "${VERSION_DIR}requirements.md"; then
      if aicoding_staged_content "${VERSION_DIR}requirements.md" | grep -q 'GWT-REQ-C'; then
        aicoding_gate_log_warning "${f}: _change_level=minor 但 requirements 存在 REQ-C，建议升级为 major 并执行 spotcheck"
      fi
    fi
  else
    DELIVERY_MISSING=""
    for doc in review_testing.md test_report.md; do
      aicoding_staged_exists "${VERSION_DIR}${doc}" || DELIVERY_MISSING="${DELIVERY_MISSING}\n  - ${doc}"
    done
    if [ -n "$DELIVERY_MISSING" ]; then
      echo "❌ 交付关口（wait_confirm/done）：以下必要产出物缺失："
      echo -e "$DELIVERY_MISSING"
      exit 1
    fi

    aicoding_run_gate critical "delivery:review-testing" validate_review_summary_and_coverage "${VERSION_DIR}review_testing.md" "${VERSION_DIR}requirements.md" "$STATUS_CURRENT_REF" || exit 1
    aicoding_run_gate critical "delivery:test-report" validate_test_report_gwt_coverage "${VERSION_DIR}requirements.md" "${VERSION_DIR}test_report.md" || exit 1
    aicoding_run_gate critical "delivery:human-spotcheck" validate_human_spotcheck "${VERSION_DIR}review_testing.md" "${VERSION_DIR}requirements.md" "$STATUS_CURRENT_REF" "$CHANGE_LEVEL" || exit 1
  fi
done <<< "$STATUS_FILES"

# --- W17 硬拦截: plan.md 任务验证命令检查 ---
PLAN_FILES=$(echo "$STAGED" | grep 'plan\.md$' || true)
if [ -n "$PLAN_FILES" ]; then
  while IFS= read -r pf; do
    [ -z "$pf" ] && continue
    PLAN_CONTENT=$(aicoding_staged_content "$pf")
    [ -z "$PLAN_CONTENT" ] && continue

    MISSING=$(echo "$PLAN_CONTENT" | awk '
      function flush() {
        if(task_title!="" && !has_cmd) {
          missing++
          print "  - " task_title
        }
      }
      /^### (T[0-9]+|任务)/{
        flush()
        task_title=$0
        has_cmd=0
        in_verify=0
        next
      }
      /验证方式/ {in_verify=1}
      in_verify && /人工确认|N\/A|NA（文档类任务）|文档类任务/ {has_cmd=1}
      in_verify && /^- *命令：/{
        if(match($0, /`[^`]+`/)) {
          cmd=substr($0, RSTART+1, RLENGTH-2)
          gsub(/^[ \t]+|[ \t]+$/, "", cmd)
          if(cmd!="" && cmd!="..." && cmd !~ /^<[^>]+>$/) has_cmd=1
        }
      }
      END{
        flush()
      }
    ')

    if [ -n "$MISSING" ]; then
      echo "❌ [W17 硬拦截] 关键节点提交被阻止：plan.md 存在缺少验证命令的任务（请在\"验证方式\"中补充可复现命令）"
      echo "$MISSING" | head -20
      exit 1
    fi
  done <<< "$PLAN_FILES"
fi

# --- Git-Hook 新增: 文档作用域校验（与 CC Gate 3 对齐，堵住 git commit 绕过）---
DOC_FILES=$(echo "$STAGED" | grep -E '^docs/v[0-9]+\.[0-9]+/' || true)
if [ -n "$DOC_FILES" ]; then
  while IFS= read -r df; do
    [ -z "$df" ] && continue
    DF_VERSION_DIR=$(echo "$df" | grep -oE 'docs/v[0-9]+\.[0-9]+/')
    [ -z "$DF_VERSION_DIR" ] && continue
    DF_STATUS="${DF_VERSION_DIR}status.md"
    DF_PHASE=$(aicoding_staged_content "$DF_STATUS" | awk '
      NR==1 && $0!="---" {exit}
      NR==1 {next}
      /^---$/ {exit}
      /^_phase:/ {sub(/^_phase:[[:space:]]*/, ""); gsub(/[[:space:]]+$/, ""); print; exit}
    ')
    [ -z "$DF_PHASE" ] && continue
    case "$DF_PHASE" in
      "Change Management"|ChangeManagement) DF_ALLOWED="status.md|review_|cr/" ;;
      Proposal)       DF_ALLOWED="status.md|proposal.md|review_|cr/" ;;
      Requirements)   DF_ALLOWED="status.md|requirements.md|proposal.md|review_|cr/" ;;
      Design)         DF_ALLOWED="status.md|design.md|review_|cr/" ;;
      Planning)       DF_ALLOWED="status.md|plan.md|review_|cr/" ;;
      Implementation) DF_ALLOWED="status.md|review_|cr/|plan.md|tasks/|design.md|requirements.md" ;;
      Testing)        DF_ALLOWED="status.md|test_report.md|review_|cr/|design.md|requirements.md|spotcheck_" ;;
      Deployment)     DF_ALLOWED="status.md|deployment.md|test_report.md|review_|cr/|spotcheck_" ;;
      *) continue ;;
    esac
    DF_BASENAME=$(basename "$df")
    DF_MATCH=false
    for pat in $(echo "$DF_ALLOWED" | tr '|' ' '); do
      case "$pat" in
        */) echo "$df" | grep -q "/${pat}" && { DF_MATCH=true; break; } ;;
        *)  [ "$DF_BASENAME" = "$pat" ] && { DF_MATCH=true; break; }
            echo "$DF_BASENAME" | grep -q "^${pat}" && { DF_MATCH=true; break; } ;;
      esac
    done
    if [ "$DF_MATCH" = false ]; then
      echo "❌ 文档作用域校验：当前阶段 ${DF_PHASE}，不允许提交 ${df}。本阶段允许：${DF_ALLOWED//|/, }"
      exit 1
    fi
  done <<< "$DOC_FILES"
fi

# --- Git-Hook 5: git config 防篡改 ---
if echo "$STAGED" | grep -qE '(^|/)\.gitconfig$|(^|/)\.gitmodules$'; then
  echo "❌ 检测到 git 配置文件变更，需人工确认"
  exit 1
fi

aicoding_gate_log_pass "pre-commit"
exit 0
